                            <comment id="16287226" author="jay.zhuang" created="Tue, 12 Dec 2017 07:26:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed the failed unittest and added an uTest for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14090&quot; title=&quot;stress.generate.Distribution.average broken on trunk&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-14090&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-14090&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, please review:&lt;/p&gt;
